               <p>SEVENTH DAY, WEDNESDAY, FEBRUARY 27, 1822.</p>
               <p>392. 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-67-defend743" type="defendantName">
                     WILLIAM 
                     LILL
                  <interp inst="t18220220-67-defend743" type="surname" value="LILL"></interp>
