             was indicted for <rs id="t18220220-67-off358" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-67-off358" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-67-off358" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220220-67-cd359" type="crimeDate">7th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-67-off358 t18220220-67-cd359"></join>, one coat, value 10 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-67-victim745" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Lovat
                  <interp inst="t18220220-67-victim745" type="surname" value="Lovat"></interp>
