                     <interp inst="t18220220-67-person748" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am clerk to Mr. 
               <persName id="t18220220-67-person749">
                  Samuel 
                  Lovat
               <interp inst="t18220220-67-person749" type="surname" value="Lovat"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-67-person749" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-67-person749" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , this is his bar coat.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went and enquired for Priestley, and as I returned, in Carey-street a boy overtook me with the coat; I bought it of him for 2 s. 6 d.</p>
